title: Records most likely to be broken
itunes:title: Records most likely to be broken
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss the latest news around the NFL including Colin Kaepernick's offseason workouts and Rob Gronkowski's latest whereabouts. The guys then debate which current players are most likely to break prominent NFL records.
